     ## Key Milestones in 2024-2025
     
     | Date | Milestone |
     |------|-----------|
     | **Dec 2024** | Factorial unveiled first A-sample 40Ah Solstice all-solid-state cells |
     | **Dec 2024** | Lithium-metal SSB installed in Mercedes EQS for testing |
     | **2024** | Honda opened prototype solid-state battery production facility |
     | **Jan 2024** | China established CASIP (All-Solid-State Battery Collaborative Innovation Platform) |
